Appreciation post 💕 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ 
Thank you. For letting me be me and find my way. For always supporting me, even when it might feel hard. We may not always agree on things and we’re not perfect, but at the end of the day we always choose each other. We always have each others back. For that, I’m so grateful. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ 

I Love You @lylebeniga 😘
Merry Christmas friends, from our family to yours❤️. I’m so very blessed to have these two. My rocks, my boys, my everything. 🥹🥰🎄

Happiest Birthday to my love @lylebeniga ❤️! You are the voice of reason, the one who makes us feel safe, my best friend, the King of our hearts 💕. Kwes and I love you so much and are so grateful you were born on this day!! Our world would not be the same without you in it 🥹❤️. HAPPY BIRTHDAY!! Can’t wait to celebrate, just the two of us 😘.
🐇slope or snow 🐇? ☺️ Valentine’s Day with my one and only on the mountain today 💕. I love you @lylebeniga !!
Lately 🌷
Got to witness the cherry blossoms in bloom today in DC with the family 🌸. It’s such a special thing to experience, so glad I got to share it with loved ones 🥹❤️.
Spring break in the snow babyyy, we’re gettin kinda nice out here on these slopes 🤙🏻🤙🏾. ⛷️🏂
Happy Easter! It was a beautiful day with family and friends 🌷🐣🐇
Forever holding my boy like a baby. I can’t believe he’s going to be 4 🥹❤️

It’s really hard as parents not to keep score of the jobs/efforts that we put into our family. Parenting can feel so overwhelming at times, and is certainly a job in itself. However, when you have the support of a partner whose role is equally as important as yours, it makes the journey so much better. Sure it’s not always perfect, but that’s what makes us stronger.

 Your presence in our sons life @lylebeniga, the passionate work ethic you model, the long sleepless work trips when you still make time to FaceTime every waking moment you’re free, the coming home and immediately jumping into fatherhood and playtime, your attentiveness to Kwes when you’re together, and the constant hustle to provide the absolute best life for our family is immeasurable. We are so so blessed to have you, I could not imagine this life without you in it. We celebrate you today yes, but please always remember that we celebrate you every single day. We love you so much babe! Happy Fathers Day ❤️

Hi friends, as some of you know, my hometown of Montpelier, Vermont was recently devastated by severe flooding. Many and most of the small local businesses in town have been drastically affected by this. If you’ve ever been to Montpelier or Vermont you know that what makes our home special are the local businesses. Sharing this for awareness as well as any donations that could be made. I will also be linking another relief fund in my bio called Montpelier alive, this fund will help to support the local businesses to get back on their feet. Thank you all! ❤️ https://www.gofundme.com/f/minikin-shoppe-flood-relief-montpelier-vt?utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet&utm_medium=copy_link_all&utm_source=customer
